name: TERIMA KASIH
description:
This is a special artwork for celebrating 1.000 FOLLOWERS ON TWITTER. 

There is a legend that says "when you continue to work with high dedication, then with that you thank your God for the gifts given". I dedicate this work to the people who have helped me to grow. Grow without coercion. Grow with hope. May we all grow well together. Thank you :)

5000 x 5000 PX
